# === BEFORE MAKING THIS REPO PUBLIC ===
# Today (2026-04-27) this repo is private and context/CONSTRAINTS.md is tracked
# so agents can read it from the filesystem. If/when this repo goes public:
#
#   1. Uncomment the `context/CONSTRAINTS.md` line below — CONSTRAINTS.md
#      contains approval gates, the trip wire, and customer-data rules.
#      Not safe in a public repo.
#   2. Move the contents of context/CONSTRAINTS.md into Doppler under a
#      key the CEO and managers load from the environment, not the filesystem.
#   3. Re-audit /context/Daniel.md, /context/Ohanafy.md, /context/STACK.md
#      for customer-sensitive content (Gulf Distributing details, customer
#      lists, integration partner names) before publishing.
#   4. Confirm /coaching/<agent-id>/history.md (once populated) does not
#      contain anything customer-sensitive.
# ======================================

